‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Ecommerce.API/       ‚Üê ASP.NET Core Web API (Presentation Layer)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Ecommerce.Application/ ‚Üê Application Layer (Use Cases / Services)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Ecommerce.Domain/      ‚Üê Domain Layer (Entities / Business Logic)
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Ecommerce.Infrastructure/ ‚Üê Infrastructure Layer (DB, Repositories)
Command 1:
dotnet new sln -n EcommerceApp


‚úÖ What happened:

You created a Solution file (EcommerceApp.sln).

A solution is like a ‚Äúcontainer‚Äù that organizes multiple projects.

It helps you manage relationships between projects ‚Äî like your main API, domain library, and data layer.

